00:40:12,000 --> 00:40:12,440
What?

858
00:40:13,190 --> 00:40:14,050
They're saying

859
00:40:14,210 --> 00:40:17,810
Tietou knocked Silly Tiao up.

860
00:40:22,450 --> 00:40:23,590
You're such a young girl.

861
00:40:23,590 --> 00:40:25,280
How could you say something so vulgar?

862
00:40:25,280 --> 00:40:25,800
Mother,

863
00:40:25,960 --> 00:40:26,960
I trust Tietou.

864
00:40:27,180 --> 00:40:28,710
Don't listen to that.

865
00:40:31,590 --> 00:40:32,790
How did it go, Father?

866
00:40:33,000 --> 00:40:34,000
Did you get the medicine?

867
00:40:34,000 --> 00:40:35,030
Good grief,

868
00:40:35,800 --> 00:40:36,730
Ning Xuexiang is

869
00:40:36,840 --> 00:40:38,670
such a fickle miser.

870
00:40:39,960 --> 00:40:42,190
A few days ago, he'd lend us anything

871
00:40:42,550 --> 00:40:44,800
and even offered prescriptions.

872
00:40:44,920 --> 00:40:46,630
But today, not only did he refuse,

873
00:40:46,630 --> 00:40:49,440
he also said that our family

874
00:40:49,440 --> 00:40:52,000
owes him—rent and silver—

875
00:40:53,190 --> 00:40:54,320
do you know how much?

876
00:40:54,670 --> 00:40:56,920
12 silver dollars!

877
00:40:59,230 --> 00:41:00,420
It's all my fault.

878
00:41:03,280 --> 00:41:04,940
I don't want to live anymore.

879
00:41:05,230 --> 00:41:05,880
Mother,

880
00:41:06,190 --> 00:41:07,230
don't worry.

881
00:41:07,670 --> 00:41:08,710
I still have ways.

882
00:41:09,530 --> 00:41:10,930
I'll think of something.

883
00:41:11,510 --> 00:41:12,550
I will.

884
00:41:14,630 --> 00:41:16,030
I will.

885
00:41:21,230 --> 00:41:22,690
We were only gone for a day,

886
00:41:22,880 --> 00:41:24,140
and all this happened?

887
00:41:24,840 --> 00:41:26,320
Did you ask Silly Tiao

888
00:41:26,560 --> 00:41:27,560
who did it?

889
00:41:28,800 --> 00:41:29,590
Ask her? How?

890
00:41:30,400 --> 00:41:31,460
With the way she is,

891
00:41:32,010 --> 00:41:32,710
the moment I ask,

892
00:41:32,710 --> 00:41:34,570
all she says is I braided her hair.

893
00:41:34,720 --> 00:41:36,120
I don't dare get near her.

894
00:41:41,350 --> 00:41:42,140
Silly Tiao.

895
00:41:46,280 --> 00:41:47,000
Silly Tiao.

896
00:41:48,630 --> 00:41:49,590
Tell me,

897
00:41:50,030 --> 00:41:51,030
who hurt you?

898
00:41:53,100 --> 00:41:54,020
Talk to me.

899
00:41:56,960 --> 00:41:58,320
Bride.

900
00:41:59,550 --> 00:42:00,400
Talk to me.

901
00:42:00,630 --> 00:42:01,400
I want buns.

902
00:42:02,800 --> 00:42:03,460
I want buns.

903
00:42:03,940 --> 00:42:05,270
Okay, you can have buns.

904
00:42:05,820 --> 00:42:07,190
Tell me who hurt you,

905
00:42:07,190 --> 00:42:08,530
and I'll give you buns, okay?

906
00:42:08,530 --> 00:42:09,940
I want buns.

907
00:42:10,010 --> 00:42:12,050
What bun? We don't have any buns.

908
00:42:13,600 --> 00:42:15,770
If you want one, go back to your own home.

909
00:42:15,770 --> 00:42:18,040
Please leave. I'm begging you.

910
00:42:18,070 --> 00:42:19,800
Can't you just go home?

911
00:42:19,820 --> 00:42:21,440
Auntie.

912
00:42:21,930 --> 00:42:22,290
You…

913
00:42:22,320 --> 00:42:22,780
Auntie.

914
00:42:23,150 --> 00:42:24,590
Auntie, don't yell at her.

915
00:42:24,590 --> 00:42:26,190
Yelling won't solve anything.

916
00:42:26,190 --> 00:42:28,000
What did I do

917
00:42:28,000 --> 00:42:29,150
to deserve all this?

918
00:42:29,240 --> 00:42:31,240
How am I supposed to live with this?

919
00:42:31,400 --> 00:42:32,320
Calm down.

920
00:42:32,320 --> 00:42:33,400
Go back inside.

921
00:42:33,720 --> 00:42:34,110
Look at her.

922
00:42:34,110 --> 00:42:34,970
Go back inside.

923
00:42:39,400 --> 00:42:39,920
Xiuxiu.

924
00:42:40,510 --> 00:42:40,970
Dajiao.

925
00:42:41,920 --> 00:42:43,580
You two believe me, don't you?

926
00:42:43,840 --> 00:42:45,630
What's the use of us believing you?

927
00:42:45,630 --> 00:42:47,830
What matters is figuring out the truth.

928
00:42:48,550 --> 00:42:50,800
Tietou, braid my hair.

929
00:42:50,840 --> 00:42:52,320
Stay away from me.

930
00:42:52,440 --> 00:42:53,440
Stay away from me.

931
00:42:54,030 --> 00:42:54,960
Dajiao, Dajiao.

932
00:42:55,070 --> 00:42:55,550
Silly Tiao.

933
00:42:55,550 --> 00:42:56,320
Silly Tiao.

934
00:42:56,320 --> 00:42:56,960
Stop it. Stop it.

935
00:42:56,960 --> 00:42:58,630
Buns. Buns. Buns.

936
00:42:59,400 --> 00:42:59,840
Buns.

937
00:43:01,010 --> 00:43:02,110
I'll go get one for you.

938
00:43:02,110 --> 00:43:03,030
Don't move.

939
00:43:03,110 --> 00:43:04,030
Buns, buns.

940
00:43:05,440 --> 00:43:06,220
Let's wait here.

941
00:43:06,220 --> 00:43:07,820
We'll wait here for the buns.

942
00:43:08,590 --> 00:43:09,140
Come.

